    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Devotional book containing selections from the Qurʼān, several illuminated seals (muhr) and calligraphic drawings with the names of God, the Prophet Muḥammad, other Imams and family members; three blank pages at the end have been prepared for drawing but left unfilled (f. 69v-70v).</subfield>
    </datafield>
